Cell["\<\
Construct the Rabi Hamiltonian. Note that the photon-qubit coupling includes \
the so-called counter-rotating terms. Note that the model is not exactly \
solvable (in fact, there exits a exact solution, but is not of simple form).\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1276888457,ExpressionUUID->"0e193da3-d798-41ce-9ee7-a0f35ee05af0"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"ham", "=", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
